comments.body:
And to be clear, this is about the groups, not the values themselves? i.e.
{noformat}
keys   = [0,   0,    1,   1,   null]
values = ["a", null, "b", "b", "c"]{noformat}
should give
{noformat}
counts = {0: 2, 1: 1} {noformat}
instead of
{noformat}
counts = {0: 2, 1: 1, null: 1} {noformat}
?
